HEADWORD: Morkin
<hw>Mor"kin</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Akin to Sw.
<ets>murken</ets> putrefied, Icel. <ets>morkinn</ets> putrid.]</ety>
<def>A beast that has died of disease or by mischance.</def>
